      • predict

        public void predict​(@Nullable
                    float[] numericFeatures,
                    @Nullable
                    int[] catFeatureHashes,
                    @NotNull
                    CatBoostPredictions prediction)
             throws ai.catboost.CatBoostError
        Same as predict(float[], String[], CatBoostPredictions), but accept categoric features as hashes computed by hashCategoricalFeature(String).
        パラメータ:
        numericFeatures - Numeric features.
        catFeatureHashes - Categoric feature hashes.
        prediction - Model predictions.
        例外:
        ai.catboost.CatBoostError - In case of error within native library.
